  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President leaves the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Katunayake airport sources said that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has left for Maldives this morning.",
        "The President, his wife and one of their security officers have left.",
        "It is reported that a group of Sri Lankan Air Force officers took and approved the passports and other essential documents of the four persons to the immigration department officials at the Katunayake airport departure terminal.",
        "They left the Katunayake Air Force Base at around 01.45 this morning in a Antonov-32 (AN-32) type aircraft belonging to the Sri Lanka Air Force.",
        "The BBC reported that Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa left the country in a military jet.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa arrived in Mal\u00e9, the capital of the Maldives, at around 3 am today, BBC News reported."
      ],
